entry.string:
apiVersion: v1 kind: Pod spec: containers: - name: maven image: maven:3.9.11-eclipse-temurin-21 command: - sleep args: - infinity securityContext: # maven runs as root by default, it is recommended or even mandatory in some environments (such as pod security admission "restricted") to run as a non-root user. runAsUser: 0 - name: docker image: docker:28.3-dind command: - dockerd args: - --host=tcp://0.0.0.0:2375 - --iptables=false # Disable iptables env: - name: DOCKER_HOST value: tcp://0.0.0.0:2375 securityContext: # ubuntu runs as root by default, it is recommended or even mandatory in some environments (such as pod security admission "restricted") to run as a non-root user. privileged: true
- name: kubectl image: bitnami/kubectl:latest command: ["sleep"] args: ["infinity"] tty: true

docker build -t samuelcavalcanti/quickstart:10 . docker login -u samuelcavalcanti -p ${REGISTRY_PASSWORD} docker tag samuelcavalcanti/quickstart:10 samuelcavalcanti/quickstart:latest docker push samuelcavalcanti/quickstart:10 docker push samuelcavalcanti/quickstart:latest
